sequenceDiagram
    participant Client
    participant API
    participant PaymentService
    participant Logger
    participant Database
    
    Client->>API: POST /payment
    API->>Logger: Log request
    API->>PaymentService: Process payment
    
    alt Success
        PaymentService->>Database: Save transaction
        Database-->>PaymentService: OK
        PaymentService-->>API: Payment successful
        API->>Logger: Log success
        API-->>Client: 200 OK
    else Error
        PaymentService-->>API: Payment failed
        API->>Logger: Log error
        API-->>Client: 400 Error
    end
